### Criar usuário
POST http://localhost:8000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Marina Costa",
  "email": "marina.costa@cloudflow.local",
  "password": "Senha123",
  "role": "admin"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "marina.costa@cloudflow.local",
  "password": "Senha123"
}

### Criar fluxo
POST http://localhost:8000/workflows
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Aprovação de compra de notebooks",
  "description": "Fluxo interno para análise e aprovação de equipamentos.",
  "status": "open",
  "priority": "high",
  "owner_id": 1
}
